<p><strong>总结：</strong> vue3.0 封装组件支持 v-model 的时候，父传子<code>:modelValue</code> 子传父 <code>@update:modelValue</code></p>
<p><strong>补充：</strong> vue2.0 的 <code>xxx.sync</code> 语法糖解析 父传子 <code>:xxx</code> 子传父 <code>@update:xxx</code> 在 vue3.0 使用 <code>v-model:xxx</code> 代替。</p>
<h2 id="_18-mixins-语法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_18-mixins-语法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 18-mixins 语法</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>目标：掌握 mixins 语法的基本使用，vue2.x 封装逻辑的方式，vue3.0 建议使用组合 API</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">官方话术：</p>
<p>混入 (mixin) 提供了一种非常灵活的方式，来分发 Vue 组件中的可复用功能。一个混入对象可以包含任意组件选项。当组件使用混入对象时，所有混入对象的选项将被“混合”进入该组件本身的选项。</p>
</div>
<ul>
<li>理解<strong>全局混入</strong>：<strong>所有组件</strong>混入了这些逻辑代码</li>
</ul>
<details class="custom-container details"><summary>全局 mixin</summary>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// 全局混入 全局mixin</span>
<span class="token comment">// vue2.0 写法  Vue.mixin({})</span>
app<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">mixin</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token literal-property property">methods</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token function">say</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
      console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>$el<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"在mounted中调用say函数"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
  <span class="token function">mounted</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">say</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br><span class="line-number">9</span><br><span class="line-number">10</span><br><span class="line-number">11</span><br><span class="line-number">12</span><br></div></div></details>
<ul>
